title: The Alysia Magen Interview: Fighting Blac Chyna, Kicked out of the Military for Onlyfans & More
description:
Alysia Magen talks about bodybuilding, why she left the Air Force, the Black Chyna fight and much more!

-----
00:00 Intro
1:26 Growing up in a tiny little town in Nebraska, kinda poor, in a trailer 
3:33 Late bloomer, going to church schools, kinda shy 
4:21 Got hot senior year and was still a virgin at that time, lost her virginity to r**
5:38 Going to the military to be independent and to grow up 
8:48 Her body is all natural! Was super heavy into bodybuilding, took steroids 
9:51 She was super unhealthy then, too skinny, didn't get her period for 2 years 
18:14 Alysia was released from the military, for doing her thing on the side, selling waist trainers, fitness stuff etc 
20:02 She was well-liked, really didn't understand why it took such a turn. Literally got Article 15 after doing a side-by-side on IG, (work uniform vs bikini photo) 
21:38 The attorney couldn't believe why she was asked to leave she had a perfect record
23:32 Came to LA after that and got lost in terms of human interactions, just super depressed
25:17 The Black Chyna situation, Alysia got hit up to fight her she was down right way
26:54 Only had a month and a half to prep and train 
28:17 Black Chyna was a sore loser and got mad every time the bell rang, her trainer tried to fight Alysia after the fight was over
31:44 Alysia dropped a Black Chyna diss track 
33:01 Alysia feels better, got away from toxic situations, and loves fighting, might stay in that lane with more time to prep next time
33:55 Is she gonna make her OF more wild or nah?
37:50 Alysia got a lot of stalkers, one came to her house to marry her, she called the cops, he actually was an army vet 
42:30 Adam asks if he can be "top white boy" coming for Jack Harlow spot, Eminem is goat white boy
-----
